critter.name: Queen Alexandra's Birdwing
critter.desc: Hoo! The horror! This behemoth butterfly may be a Queen Alexandra’s birdwing... But I call it Queen of My Nightmares! It is huge! Indeed, the world’s hugest. No butterfly can beat its foot-long wingspan. The larvae alone grow to more than 4 inches. As if it weren’t appalling enough...they’re poisonous! Murderous monsters, indeed!
critter.quote: I caught a Queen Alexandra’s birdwing! That‘s a feather in my cap!
